Unknown gunmen have killed the owner of Falola Hotel and Rental Services, Falola Oke in Ilesa, Osun State, on Wednesday. Falola, was reportedly killed beside his house on Wednesday night in Ilesa. It was gathered that Falola was killed around 9pm around Fadahunsi street, Imon area, Ilesa. When contacted, Public Relations Officer of the state Police Command, Yemisi Opalola, confirmed the incident. She asserted that the command has commenced investigation on the killing.